"freebsd                                      1  1024     1     -b----   663.9\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/virtualization/_index.adoc:1106
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"To begin the installation of the base operating system, start the VNC "
